	// ---------- Fish Descriptions ----------
	// SVE - fish
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Andy": "This sponge becomes a bit red when you keep poking at it.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Apples": "It can easily be mistaken with an unripe cherry.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Claire": "An elegant fish who likes to spin in water currents.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Gunther": "Its tendency to wrap around lost treasures makes it a perfect archaeologist friend.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Henchman": "It ferociously defends its home against any intruders.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Lance": "This proud seahorse parades around divers, defending them from the aggressive fauna.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Marlon": "It can be seen grabbing sharp rocks and corals in its jaws to defend itself.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Martin": "A shy starfish who often observes other fish swimming around.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Morgan": "It is often seen in very deep meditation.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Morris": "This fish uses its big body to intimidate other fish into giving it their shinies.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Olivia": "This big fish ostensibly shows off its pretty scales shining under the sun.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Scarlett": "An energetic fish who likes to be petted.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Sophia": "A timid fish who hates to be touched.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Susan": "This friendly little fish seems ready to help despite its small size.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Victor": "It likes to nest into holes left by fallen bricks in bridges.",
	// SVE - crabpot
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Alesia": "Hmm yummy drink-! Oh wait no, that's a living creature.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Axel": "It's not easy to catch it alone, without its cast.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Brooklyn": "It's not easy to catch it alone, without its cast.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Camilla": "Any fish that crosses its path ends up following it, completely charmed.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Chloe": "It's not easy to catch it alone, without its cast.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Dusty": "It only got caught because its ball was stuck in the pot and it wouldn't leave it alone.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Gil": "Is it sleeping or are its eyes naturally closed?",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.HighlandsDwarf": "This creature made its home from an old bottle and a discarded helmet.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Isaac": "Its sharp protuberance almost broke the crab pot!",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Jace": "It's not easy to catch it alone, without its cast.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Jadu": "Its weird round shape allows it to zoom across the oceans.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Jolyne": "It may looks like a curious flower, but this creature can be quite ferocious.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Mermaid": "This songstress has a voice that resounds far beyond what its small shell implies.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Peaches": "It got separated from its Tadpples friend at some point.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.SVE.Zoey": "It's not easy to catch it alone, without its cast.",

	// ---------- Note Titles ----------
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote1": "Lurker in the river",
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote2": "A cherry fish?",
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote3": "Notice from Joja Mart",
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote4": "Artifact finder eel",
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote5": "Seahorse in the forest",
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote6": "More magic fish",
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote7": "Notice from Joja Plumbing Inc. 2",
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote8": "Journey to the bridge",
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote9": "Friendly couple of fish",
	"NPCFish.title.SVEFishNote10": "Shipping bin!",

	// ---------- Hint ----------
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote1": "Something's been lurking in the river behind my house. The strawberries are a lot of work already, I don't need another thing to be wary of!",
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote2": "I saw what seemed to be an unripe cherry in the pond in this weird clearing south of Cindersap, but when sun shone down on it it began to swam around! Probably another 'weird fish'.",
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote3": "Attention to all employees: curious new life forms have been spotted in the pond in front of the mart, in summer during the heatwave and in fall. They are only two for now, but please warn your supperior if you notice any multiplication of these 'fish'.",
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote4": "I found a new artifact lost to the water just below the bridge - kneeling in the snow to catch it was not the best experience. I only noticed it because what looked like a curious eel had wrapped around it.",
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote5": "There are a lot of curious things in the highlands, but I never would have expected to see a seahorse! It was majestic, parading under the sun, flower petals all around... And what flamboyant fins!",
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote6": "There seems to be more magic-sensible fish than first thought. Two of them causes disturbance during the rain, in the swamp and the deep forest. The last one seems to hunt when the water are freezing, around the waterfall next to the guild. Please report any change of behaviours.",
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote7": "Note from Joja Plumbing Inc.: We really need to be careful with this next intervention; it's at one of the mart manager's house. It's the same thing as last time: weird gurgling sound in the pipes. I swear I'll ask to never be assigned to this town again.",
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote8": "I went to check on Victor, who had spent the entire day under the rain at the bridge, and he told me he think he saw a fish in the waters there. It was clear once we went back home, and I think I saw sparkling scales when crossing the old comunity garden, just over the fence. Probably another curious fish.",
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote9": "I think I saw one back at home when taking a walk for my birthday - just enjoying the sun! And last time, I came to visit Sophia, I spotted another one which looked very similar!",
	"NPCFish.Hint.SVEFishNote10": "There is a fish in my shipping bin!"
}
